title: Royal Sweets Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Delivery, Take-out, Catering
description: Samosa, pakoras, onion bhaji, chats, naan, roti, thali and Punjabi curries including aloo gobhi, vegetable korma, spinach with cheese and cury cottage cheese. Many vegan options (without ghee). Also Indian sweets including galub jaman, ladoo, halva. Free home delivery local area over $30 between 6-9pm.
